14 Underwood Avenue, Botany also known as 8 Byrnes Street is a very well positioned high clearance warehouse with two (2) street frontage. 

Within vicinity of Port Botany and Sydney Airport, and close access to the Eastern Distributor and the M5 Motorway. 

- 883sqm* GLA
- Dual street access from Underwood Avenue and Byrnes Street
- High clearance warehousing
- Ample off-street parking 
- Container accessible 
- Refurbished offices and amenities 
- Available 1st July 2021

CBRE is pleased to present 19 Clevedon Street, Botany to the market For Lease. The property is an extremely well-presented freestanding industrial factory located in the Port Botany precinct. Clevedon Street provides immediate access to Port Botany, Sydney Airport and the Sydney CBD with arterial road links connecting to wider Sydney via the M1 and M5 Motorways.

Property Highlights:
+ 785sqm Freestanding industrial factory
+ Modern, air conditioned office
+ High clearance, column free warehouse
+ High amp 3-Phase power 
+ Immaculate amenities
+ Flexible Zoning
+ Off-street parking
+ 169m* to nearest bus stop
+ Container height roller shutter doors

For more information and to arrange an inspection, please contact the exclusive CBRE listing agents.
